feat(workshop): add PositionPicker.svelte (Scene 7) with cascading book/chapter dropdowns

Replaces the inline number-input picker in Workshop with a dedicated
PositionPicker component. Dropdowns are populated from the DB (books
table + chapters filtered by selected book). Chapter list resets when
the book changes. ESC and backdrop click close without saving; Update
persists to localStorage, updates the URL pos param, closes the overlay,
and triggers a panel refetch if a theory is set.
